<li>"<a href="http://www.cosmopolis.ch/english/art/68/qing_art.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.cosmopolis.ch/english/art/68/qing_art.htm" rel="nofollow">Qing art of the reigns of the Kangxi, Yongzhen and Qianlong Emperors</a>." Retrieved on 2008-11-10.</li>
<li>Section on the Ming and Qing dynasties of "<a href="http://afe.easia.columbia.edu/china/geog/population.htm#2b" class="external text" title="http://afe.easia.columbia.edu/china/geog/population.htm#2b" rel="nofollow">China's Population: Readings and Maps</a>." Retrieved on 2008-11-10.</li>
<li>"<a href="http://drben.net/ChinaReport/Sources/History/Qing/Descendancy_Summary_Qing_Dynasty_1644-1911AD.html" class="external text" title="http://drben.net/ChinaReport/Sources/History/Qing/Descendancy_Summary_Qing_Dynasty_1644-1911AD.html" rel="nofollow">Short History &amp; Time-Line of the Qing Dynasty</a>."</li>
<li><a href="http://www.history-of-china.com/qing-dynasty/kangxi-emperor.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.history-of-china.com/qing-dynasty/kangxi-emperor.htm" rel="nofollow">Kangxi Emperor</a></li>
